# Three-Address Code (TAC) - Unoptimized

 1: FUNC_BEGIN Master
 2: DECL float pi
 3: pi = 3.14
 4: PRINT pi
 5: DECL float two_pi
 6: t0 = pi + pi
 7: two_pi = t0
 8: PRINT two_pi
 9: DECL float x
10: x = 1.5
11: DECL float y
12: y = 2.5
13: DECL float z
14: t1 = x + y
15: z = t1
16: PRINT z
17: FUNC_END Master
